Class Story

java.lang.Object
  edu.ualberta.utils.Story

public class Story
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents the "book cover" of the story for the most part, and as such, most of the functionality in this class is actually just wrappers around functions in Page.java. Refer to that for further information.
